Detailed Description

Exception in the simulation process.

This class abstract the behaviour of an exception in the EDLUT simulation process. This exception could happen by different reasons (not found files, bad input spikes, not enough memory...). When an exception is thrown, the simulation is stopped without results.

Author:
Jesus Garrido

Richard Carrillo
